    <item>
      <title>Mercenaries of Nightshift - Karana Server [Updated with Charter]</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Karana&amp;message.id=121#M121</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;U&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=center&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=center&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial size=6&gt;Charter for Mercenaries&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=center&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial size=6&gt;of Nightshift&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=center&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial&gt;&#xD;
&lt;HR&gt;&#xD;
&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P align=left&gt;&lt;FONT face=Arial&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Intent:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff size=3&gt;The intent of the Guild known as "Mercenaries of Nightshift" is two fold:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff size=3&gt;1) To provide a guild where 1st to 30th level (Refered to as lowbie) characters have a way of grouping with other lower level characters, join in on quests, and have more opportunities for advancement in the game.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff size=3&gt;2) Hiring out of services to other guilds / parties for barter or payment.&amp;nbsp; (explained in further detail below)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size=3&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff size=3&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;U&gt;Mercenaries Guild:&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff size=3&gt;This is the idea:&amp;nbsp; To add flavor to the game, and to generate revenue, a Guild can hire our services to help during a Raid or a Quest for a particular character.&amp;nbsp; I've noticed alot of small guilds that have low level characters whom are trying to level or even get epics, but can't due to time constraints, lack of available guildies to help with raid, or any number of other issues.&amp;nbsp; Merc's of Nightshift would act as the Character (hereto refered to as Client)'s proxy guild.&amp;nbsp; Our rates would be reasonable, payout of say 1000 plat for the services of the guild for a Raid, or 500 plat for a team of people for a specific run.&amp;nbsp; These are just off the top of my head rates, and they may change over time.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Further, in lieu of pay for services, guild would take either items, or help from said guild on our raids or runs.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Levels:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Guild will be open to all levels.&amp;nbsp; However, any character over 30+ must mentor to either one or more of their lower class counterpart.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Ex: 50th level Wizard MUST mentor at least one 1-30 level Wizard.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;The reason for this is simple:&amp;nbsp; I've been grouping alot lately and have grouped with some low level wizards who have gotten it into their heads that they are melee fighters.&amp;nbsp; I've been coming to the rescue of people who are being attacked by things WAY too big for them and as they run out of mana, attempting to kill an Orc Centurion with what is basically a butter knife after running out of shock of frost spells.&amp;nbsp; I will run a "Wizard Boot Camp" for wizards 1-10 to learn the ropes.&amp;nbsp; This is one example.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;We are still pending as a guild at this time.&amp;nbsp; If you are interested, please contact me directly via pernwen@gmail.com or reply to this thread.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Hoping to hear from folks soon,&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;Bill/Pernwen&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ffffff&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
